OL,3,CMurdered ex-prison officer's family
OL,4,Cpraised for 'determined' law change
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FThe family of a murdered former prison
OL,8,Fofficer have been praised in the House
OL,9,Fof Lords for "their dignified and
OL,10,Fdetermined advocacy" as a law change
OL,11,Faimed at deterring revenge attacks
OL,12,Ftook a step closer.
OL,14,FThe killing of Lenny Scott in
OL,15,FSkelmersdale, Lancashire, in 2024
OL,16,Fsparked demands to close a legal
OL,17,Floophole.
OL,26,@qD@NOUrD@TO]
