OL,3,CMurdered ex-prison officer's family
OL,4,Cpraised for 'determined' law change
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FThe father-of-three was shot dead by
OL,8,Farmed robber Elias Morgan for seizing
OL,9,Fan illicit phone from his jail cell
OL,10,Fyears earlier while working at HMP
OL,11,FAltcourse in Liverpool.
OL,13,FBut because Mr Scott had left the
OL,14,Fprison service by then, Morgan did not
OL,15,Fface the harshest penalty available of
OL,16,Fa whole life order, meaning he would
OL,17,Fnever be released from jail.
OL,19,FThe criminal was instead sentenced in
OL,20,FSeptember to serve a minimum of 45
OL,21,Fyears behind bars.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
