OL,3,CMurdered ex-prison officer's family
OL,4,Cpraised for 'determined' law change
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FThose who kill an on-duty prison or
OL,8,Fpolice officer can currently expect
OL,9,Fthe most severe prison sentence, where
OL,10,Fthey spend the rest of their life in
OL,11,Fjail.
OL,13,FFollowing a campaign, this will now be
OL,14,Fextended to cover offenders who murder
OL,15,Foff-duty or former officers because of
OL,16,Ftheir job.
OL,18,FProbation officers will also be
OL,19,Fbrought within the scope of the
OL,20,Fwidened sentence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
