OL,4,Cpraised for 'determined' law change
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FSpeaking at third reading of the
OL,8,FSentencing Bill, Lord Timpson said:
OL,9,F"We extended the whole life order
OL,10,Fstarting point to include the murder
OL,11,Fof probation officers, and we made
OL,12,Fsure that this extends to current or
OL,13,Fformer police, prison and probation
OL,14,Fofficers where they are murdered in
OL,15,Fconnection with their duties, even if
OL,16,Fit occurs while they are off duty or
OL,17,Fafter they have left the service.
