OL,4,Cpraised for 'determined' law change
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FThe Tory change would require the
OL,8,Fcrown court commentary to be made
OL,9,Favailable within 14 days of a request
OL,10,Fbeing received, although its release
OL,11,Fwould need judicial approval.
OL,13,FThe Bill aims to ease the crisis in
OL,14,Fprison places by providing for the
OL,15,Fearly release of criminals under
OL,16,Fenhanced supervision, curbing the use
OL,17,Fof short jail terms and strengthening
OL,18,Fcommunity punishments.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
